name: VHS Dreams #08 - Rise and Fall
description:
people, i am creating a kinda crowdfunding with my art now. my wallet suffered an error, it is impossible to recover, therefore, the hicetnunc.art/vhsdreams no longer belongs to me, neither the arts still available there. to make it worse, i'm sick, infected by Covid-19.

my computer and cell phone are broken, which makes it even less possible for me to structure a new profile. so here is the artwork(i decide to make VHS Dreams #08) so that maybe i can get a new laptop or cell phone. if you want to help me, just collect this from my new account, thanks to everyone who tried to help me!
